# 1. APPLY_TO_MAIN_SITE — 9-Step Production Deployment

The full operational checklist for production deployment is in **`APPLY_TO_MAIN_SITE.md`** (in this repo).

## Pre-Deployment Checklist

| Step | Action | Details |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **1** | **Lovable env** | Configure VITE_SUPABASE_URL, VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY, VITE_SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN, VITE_SHOPIFY_STOREFRONT_TOKEN, VITE_SITE_URL in Lovable settings |
| **2** | **Supabase redirects** | Add `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/**` to Auth allowed callbacks; set Site URL |
| **3** | **Edge SITE_URL** | Update Supabase Edge Functions secret `SITE_URL` = `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/` for COD/email links |
| **4** | **Social** | Verify Instagram bio link, WhatsApp CTA, ManyChat flows, Facebook, X, TikTok, Pinterest, YouTube all point to main site with deep links |
| **5** | **Google Merchant Center** | Ensure Shopify feed (ID 5717495012) syncs; product links use main domain; Shopping ads land on main site |
| **6** | **All pages** | Verify `/`, `/products`, `/products/[handle]`, cart, checkout, login redirects, Find My Ritual, Beauty Assistant, `/health` on main site |
| **7** | **Repo config** | In understand-project: `.env` from template; Tailwind tokens applied; workflows (deploy-health-check, sync-file-changes-to-lovable, sync-issues-prs-to-lovable) in `.github/workflows/`; `LOVABLE_WEBHOOK_URL` secret is optional (workflows skip gracefully if not set) |
| **8** | **Deploy/verify** | Push to main → Lovable deploys; run `curl -s https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/health` (expect `"status": "ok"`); smoke test homepage, products, chatbot |
| **9** | **Optional catalog sync** | If needed, run Matrixify or Edge function sync to push CSV catalog updates to Shopify; verify on main site `/products` |

- [ ] All code changes are committed and tested locally
- [ ] Linting and build pass without errors
- [ ] All environment variables are documented in `env.main-site.example`
- [ ] Design system compliance verified (see section 3 below)
- [ ] Security vulnerabilities addressed

## Production Deployment Steps

When executing a push to the main site, strictly follow these steps:

### Step 1: Lovable Environment Variables
Configure in [Lovable Settings](https://lovable.dev/projects/657fb572-13a5-4a3e-bac9-184d39fdf7e6/settings):
- `VITE_SUPABASE_URL` = `https://qqceibvalkoytafynwoc.supabase.co`
- `VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` (anon/public key from Supabase)
- `VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID` = `qqceibvalkoytafynwoc`
- `VITE_SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN` = `lovable-project-milns.myshopify.com`
- `VITE_SHOPIFY_STOREFRONT_TOKEN` (Storefront API token)
- `VITE_SHOPIFY_API_VERSION` = `2025-07`
- `VITE_SITE_URL` = `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/` (full URL with protocol for auth redirects)
- `VITE_LOVABLE_URL` = `asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app` (domain only for API calls)

### Step 2: Supabase Authentication Configuration
In [Supabase Dashboard](https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/qqceibvalkoytafynwoc) → Authentication → URL Configuration:
- Add to Redirect URLs: `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/**`
- Set Site URL: `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/`

### Step 3: Supabase Edge Functions
In Supabase → Project Settings → Edge Functions → Secrets:
- Set `SITE_URL` = `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app/`
- Ensure COD/email functions use `SITE_URL` for email links

### Step 4: Social Media & Deep Links
Update all platform links to main site:
- Instagram: bio link, story links, shoppable posts (e.g., `?intent=acne&source=ig`)
- WhatsApp: CTA links, ManyChat/webhook deep links
- Facebook: page link, shop link, Messenger bot links
- Other platforms: X, TikTok, Pinterest, YouTube

### Step 5: Google Merchant Center
- Verify product feed syncing from Shopify
- Ensure landing pages point to `https://asperbeautyshop-com.lovable.app`
- Confirm no critical errors in feed

### Step 6: Frontend Verification
Test these routes on the live site:
- `/` (home), `/products`, `/products/[handle]`
- `/mom-baby` (lifecycle nav, RTL support)
- Cart drawer/page and checkout flow
- `/health` endpoint (should return 200)
- Beauty Assistant chat widget

### Step 7: Deploy to Production
```bash
cd /path/to/understand-project
git add .
git commit -m "feat: [your changes]"
git push origin main
```
Lovable will build and deploy automatically.

### Step 8: Post-Deployment Verification
- Run health check: `npm run health` (from VIP folder)
- Verify `/health` returns 200
- Manual smoke test: home, products, cart, Beauty Assistant
- Test login redirect flow
- Verify all omnichannel integrations

### Step 9 (Optional): Catalog Sync
If updating product catalog:
```bash
node scripts/sync-shopify-catalog.js --dry-run --limit 5  # test first
node scripts/sync-shopify-catalog.js                       # full sync
```

Cross-reference **APPLY_TO_MAIN_SITE.md** for detailed instructions. Do not give generic deployment advice.

